<head>MACHINE</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>CONTRAPTION</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">器械</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>COMPLEX TOOL which HAS MANY PARTS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general term for any mechanical device, especially any such device used in weaponry, is xiè 械.</p>
<p>2. Jī 機 refers specifically to a triggering device on weapons, but also more generally to any complex mechanical device.</p>
<p>3. Yǐn 檃 refers to a mechanical device for straightening timber.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>器械</p>
<p>機器</p>
<p>機</p>
<p>機械</p>
